#X text -20 359 Crucial: [s sah_dac1 @hv_param] is totally disconnected from the audio path! It is a 'dummy' param that tells the UI generator to position the dac~ 1 output jack at the bottom of the 'sah' column. Audio still outputs via the normal [dac~ 1] object., f 32;
#X text 529 343 The atten_ prefix creates a tiny Trim pot. Notice how all three parameters here share the core name 'sah' (button_sah_adc1, atten_sah, sah_dac1)? That core name is what stacks them vertically in the same column on the panel.;
#X obj 301 215 r button_sah_adc1 @hv_param 0 1 0;
#X text 552 206 The button_ prefix creates a gate button (sends 1 when pressed and 0 when released). Perfect for triggering S&H modules;
